<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b5cadb7-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s701c–2"><num value="701c–2">§ 701c–2.</num><heading> Acquisition and sale of land</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of sections 593 to 595 of this title relating to river and harbor improvements are made applicable to works of flood control heretofore or hereafter authorized.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b5cadb8-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/act/1941-08-18/ch377/s6">Aug. 18, 1941, ch. 377, § 6</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/55/650">55 Stat. 650</ref>; <ref href="/us/act/1951-10-31/ch654/s3/6">Oct. 31, 1951, ch. 654, § 3(6)</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/65/708">65 Stat. 708</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
